# AI Copilot Operating Model

## Concept
Use AI as an operational copilot to increase leverage in executive support workflows.

## Framework

### 1. First-Draft Acceleration
Use AI to generate:
- meeting briefs
- stakeholder updates
- draft communications
- travel planning options

### 2. Human Judgment Layer
Apply discretion for:
- prioritization
- risk assessment
- tone and sensitivity
- executive decision support

### 3. Repeatable Prompt Systems
Use reusable prompt frameworks to improve consistency.

### 4. Continuous Improvement
Refine prompts based on outcomes and workflow performance.
